# Learning from Day 4 : CSS

## What is CSS ?
CSS or Cascading Stylesheet is used to make website look good and visually attractive.  
HTML provides structure while CSS provides design.  

---

## Ways to add CSS
- Inline → inside tag  
- Internal → inside `<style>`  
- External → separate `.css` file

---
## Selectors
Selectors help to choose elements:
- tag → p, h1  
- class → .box  
- id → #header

---
## Inspect Tool
We use Inspect in browser to see HTML and CSS.

---

